{"tid":1773353,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「中國已有很多錢」特朗普籲世銀停止借貸給中國","createTime":"2019-12-07T11:46:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T12:41:26.000Z","uid":278587,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9d0edfc0fdb8ae85cf68529da318af947b1a96e8","tid":1773353,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T11:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191207/large/1575686694_a4dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191207%2Flarge%2F1575686694_a4dc.jpg&h=974f167e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美兩國久久未能達成貿易協議，世界銀行日前無視華府抗議，同意每年向中國低息借貸至少10億美元（約78億港元），美國總統特朗普在社交網發文，指「中國大把錢」，呼籲世界銀行停止借貸給中國。<br />\n<br />\n世界銀行周四通過援助中國的計劃，向中國每年低息借貸10億至15億美元（約78億至117億港元）至2025年6月。在前一個五年期，世界銀行每年平均借貸18億美元（約140.4億港元）給中國，計劃指借款金額將「逐步減少」。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普周五在Twitter發文炮轟世界銀行的計劃：「為甚麼世界銀行借錢給中國？怎麼可以？中國已有很多錢，如果他們缺錢，就會製造錢。停止！」白宮和世界銀行發言人暫未回應此事。<br />\n<br />\n世界銀行在2019財政年度向中國借貸金額為13億美元（約101.4億港元），比2017財政年度的24億美元（約187.2億港元）有所減少，不過特朗普政府認為北京太富有，不應再獲得國際援助，世銀的借貸額減得太少。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191207/60351398\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191207%2F60351398&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=273324b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191207%2F60351398&h=eb9ea1dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191207/60351398</a>"},{"pid":"f75b17edee7afca319e8d894d26b422668853e0b","tid":1773353,"uid":311583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T11:48:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=7e4be9a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=4bf4c166\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a>"},{"pid":"174285824e671c4d82cad52b29e5f4c1c037be66","tid":1773353,"uid":175590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T11:48:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">128 維園見</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tM1AHsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtM1AHsT.jpg&h=51b9806f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67bdb9761c16cb79e6278e172776f86fd262b9fa","tid":1773353,"uid":187629,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T11:50:48.000Z","msg":"世界第2大經濟體wo<br />\n一帶一路wo<br />\n做咩要借人錢<br />\n岩呀"},{"pid":"89f5d2950dc6c244596bc9d76bd1f04d936fb03d","tid":1773353,"uid":22422,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T11:54:43.000Z","msg":"話自己發展中國家 點解有咁撚多錢搞一貸一賂嘅?<br />\n話自己係世界第二大經濟體 點解重問世界銀行借?"},{"pid":"98798d88c0fa9583ce5fea63af386eca1efc27f0","tid":1773353,"uid":289708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T11:56:00.000Z","msg":"其實佢仲可以話自己係發展中國家<br />\n係因為人均GDP仲係好低?"},{"pid":"430c75b0c4ece773a1c20ce766b96649f150ffd0","tid":1773353,"uid":188176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,